Stormtroopers don't get a name. They are simply a tool of the First Order. But Phasma has a name, and one young soldier wants what she has. One stormtrooper has ambition. And this ambition is on a collision course with Captain Phasma.
The voice talent is provided by members of Casting Call Club (https://castingcall.club). 

"Age of Resistance: Captain Phasma"
